lives. 
</P>
<P>
These include smog cops, street-cleaner cops, dirt cops, water cops and sky 
cops. 
</P>
<P>
Will this ever stop? 
</P>
<P>
Add the usual assortment of delighted finks and witness new horizons of "save 
us from ourselves" regulation. 
</P>
<P>
DON REED 
</P>
<P>
Santa Maria 
