Camino (10-5, 3-0) with 20 points, Travis Gilley had 16 and Glen Ankton 13. No. 
7 San Pasqual (8-5, 1-1), which was without Eric Meek (strep throat), was led 
by Bryan Banner's 20 points and 10 rebounds. 
