 Hotel Queen's Counsel: Leona Helmsley has hired Alan Dershowitz, the Harvard 
law professor who helped clear Claus von Bulow of attempted murder, to handle 
the appeal of her tax evasion conviction. Dershowitz says Helmsley's image as a 
tempestuous shrew is undeserved. 
</P>
<P>
