<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 3 
</P>
</SECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Lattice Ladder A construction worker descends a soon-to-be parking lot. 
TERESA TAMURA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
