<DOCNO> LA011190-0121 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 160522 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 11, 1990, Thursday, San Diego County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 1; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
