LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- SUITS; HISPANICS -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; HISPANICS -- 
POLITICS; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; RACIAL DISCRIMINATION; WITNESSES 
</P>
