<DOCID> 160724 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 11, 1990, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Orange County Life; Part N; Page 1; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
