commissioner in Washington's Lewis County. "We do know that we have numerous 
county roads that have to be rebuilt. This is the worst flooding everybody says 
that they have ever seen." 
</P>
<P>
The weather forecast called for another storm from the Pacific Ocean this 
weekend. 
